---
title: 2R Booking Request Lifecycle
---

flowchart TD
    A([Client: POST /api/reservations]) --> B{Online?}
    B -->|No| C[PouchDB: save pending]
    C --> D([Return: queued])

    B -->|Yes| E[Laravel: validate fields]
    E --> F{Valid?}
    F -->|No| G([422 Validation Error])

    F -->|Yes| H[Zig: validate field types]
    H --> I{Zig OK?}
    I -->|No| J([400 Bad Request])

    I -->|Yes| K[Dafny Bridge: verify slot invariant]
    K --> L{Invariant holds?}
    L -->|No| M([409 Invariant Violation])

    L -->|Yes| N[DB: SELECT overlapping FOR UPDATE]
    N --> O{Overlap?}
    O -->|Yes| P([409 Conflict])

    O -->|No| Q[C++ perf: resolve slot in memory]
    Q --> R[DB: INSERT reservation]
    R --> S[Rust: cache availability update]
    S --> T([201 Created])
